{"tid":2069210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃種人係咪世界上最低人種","createTime":"2020-06-18T08:28:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T12:56:28.000Z","uid":214007,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ba7f9b8c64f432b2403cbfd35d01bec59a6e4389","tid":2069210,"uid":214007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T08:28:59.000Z","msg":"黑人俾白人欺壓全世界聲討<br />\n香港成班黃種人上年俾白人陶輝欺壓無人出聲<br />\n仲要成班黃種警狗幫白人陶輝欺壓番黃種人<br />\n<br />\n真心上年下令開槍個個唔係陶輝係黃種狗都算<br />\n而家咁睇連丙強都唔夠膽搞陶輝<br />\n如果唔係上年一早搞左陶輝是但推個純種香港人上去都得啦<br />\n咁就唔會搞成咁 所以話白人真係好撚優越"},{"pid":"94b752b586af00eb7c12a305ba90dd3a25683221","tid":2069210,"uid":153929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:14:25.000Z","msg":"黑人&gt;黃種"},{"pid":"68deaf26cd4054ef14c60b83c18bece5893ebe20","tid":2069210,"uid":216776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94b752b586af00eb7c12a305ba90dd3a25683221","tid":2069210,"uid":153929,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:14:25.000Z","msg":"黑人&gt;黃種"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:16:58.000Z","msg":"Yellow pig<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677bbce2be96dd33a42d79dd1619644f9458d0ed","tid":2069210,"uid":280681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:26:13.000Z","msg":"黃種係唔係我唔知 總之支那種肯定係"},{"pid":"dacf537a7a900da15beb30965d84fe4fd093f77a","tid":2069210,"uid":253320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T11:59:50.000Z","msg":"J短"},{"pid":"21a6b885f77ccb962fac4a806e5b590ff470fbf8","tid":2069210,"uid":66547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T12:56:28.000Z","msg":"如果發生係非洲，鬼會理咩～<br />\n重點係個黑鬼係美國公民"}]}